Title: [ANN] MoonX
Body: You can read in part " (ii) Empowering rights by holding MM. "  MoonX would enable every family member (Moon Money holders) to make decision and vote based on smart contract which would be developed in the future. That is simple, If I am not wrong in part concluding. So for those project have interested for listed in market MoonX, they should do a "Vote thought/via Moon Money"...  #CMIIW

MoonX aim is to bring all the companies, employees and business assets into a unified blockchain ecosystem, which will support business truly efficient, clear and trustworthy. Moonx is a decentralized crypto exchange. Therefore the unique decentralized ownership of exchanges depends with brothers and sister of Moonx Family. As a result, investors, contributors, Moonx angles and traders who are on this platform will be rewarded with Moon money and then they are considered as brother and sister of MoonX family. Moonx allows family members who are the coin holders has the right to make decisions that are based on the smart contract that helps for the development of the future.
